Dear Tamar and Adam

I hope you're both very well?

I just wanted to give you a heads up that you'll be receiving an invitation=
 tomorrow for the Chelsea Flower Show on 19 May.
It seems like it will come from me, but it's actually coming from a central=
/marketing mailing address, hence I wanted to clarify personally.

From what I hear it is a unique experience and beautiful show each year, an=
d I have secured two tickets for you.
Given the high demand for this event, please can you kindly let us know by =
March 10th if you can make it via the link sent to you tomorrow.

It would be my pleasure seeing you there - and/or earlier of course !

Kindest regards,
Loicque



